Package: linux-wallpaperengine
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Wallpaper Engine for Linux
 A wallpaper rendering engine supporting Steam Workshop wallpapers
 including scenes, videos, web pages, and images.
 This package includes DDE plugin mode support (--dde-plugin).
